'''''Rad''''' ([[Croatian language|Croatian]] for ''proceedings'', ''work'') is an [[academic journal]] published by the [[Yugoslav Academy of Sciences and Arts|Yugoslav, now Croatian, Academy of Sciences and Arts]]. It was their only publication from 1867 until 1882, when each of the individual scientific sections of the academy started printing their own journals. {{As of|2014}}, over five hundred issues have been published.

